{"id": "ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 736, "displayName": {"text": "MIAN", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Minimalist Chinese restaurant specializing in Chongqing dishes, including soups & spicy fare.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25reU5rOXdOa1ZyV0U5bVRVRnljVmhNTjFWWVNWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "They serve noodles right. I especially like their braised pork noodles. I seldom find this dish in other restuarants. Their food are generally good. I give 2 stars for their service is not beasue they have bad service. It's just that they don't provide you with much services. You order your food with your phone and they bring the food to your table. They serve you water and taht's about it. This place is small so there isn't much atmosphere to talk about. But they keep this place clean.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They serve noodles right. I especially like their braised pork noodles. I seldom find this dish in other restuarants. Their food are generally good. I give 2 stars for their service is not beasue they have bad service. It's just that they don't provide you with much services. You order your food with your phone and they bring the food to your table. They serve you water and taht's about it. This place is small so there isn't much atmosphere to talk about. But they keep this place clean.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Caleb Kwok", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110355685498925007918/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJrsxKscQ_4J8CX-CGkpC9sHF6_ujqJIxdEfyftcPUGnwZv7_J=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T17:44:10.167155091Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25reU5rOXdOa1ZyV0U5bVRVRnljVmhNTjFWWVNWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25reU5rOXdOa1ZyV0U5bVRVRnljVmhNTjFWWVNWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dab650970315:0xc4883287dace2398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKYWRFNTVXRUUzUVVKWFZucFBiMGRMVWxrekxVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The food was really good and the prices were reasonable. The restaurant was clean and had a nice atmosphere. A waitress with glasses really stood out. She noticed we had a child and kindly brought plastic utensils and a plastic bib for us. The service was fast and everything came out quickly. We had a great experience and will definitely come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food was really good and the prices were reasonable. The restaurant was clean and had a nice atmosphere. A waitress with glasses really stood out. She noticed we had a child and kindly brought plastic utensils and a plastic bib for us. The service was fast and everything came out quickly. We had a great experience and will definitely come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Holly Ship", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107070860522194300051/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjdXCgOM668cBud59Ymfkwpz1ERGDyXA81c7slm8Y0qF7Ycw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-16T06:27:47.978629096Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKYWRFNTVXRUUzUVVKWFZucFBiMGRMVWxrekxVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKYWRFNTVXRUUzUVVKWFZucFBiMGRMVWxrekxVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dab650970315:0xc4883287dace2398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SMVRrMDRXRlJGTVd0SGRsWlBhSGxJWXpOdFNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing food!!! The cold noodles were mind blowing, the sweet and spicy combo really worked so well. The scipy tofu noodles were great, very filling quantity at the right price. The service is excellent too, friendly staff and the place is always bustling. Highly recommend this place if you're in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing food!!! The cold noodles were mind blowing, the sweet and spicy combo really worked so well. The scipy tofu noodles were great, very filling quantity at the right price. The service is excellent too, friendly staff and the place is always bustling. Highly recommend this place if you're in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amit Nadig", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117093998299853258304/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVM3lcvrOYWR5S7WAyXpUthYMwlRWSJzZ7KEbC_I6DUpJt-J8SKgg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-19T03:54:45.118386959Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SMVRrMDRXRlJGTVd0SGRsWlBhSGxJWXpOdFNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SMVRrMDRXRlJGTVd0SGRsWlBhSGxJWXpOdFNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dab650970315:0xc4883287dace2398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0cWFWTjFOWEZNUzFVelNVNWhNRkZaVUVOMlgyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Sichuan cold noodles tasted like they had been sitting in the fridge for a few hours—starch retrograded and the texture was off. Sauce was balanced and flavorful but the noodles were just wrong. Beef noodle soup was solidly fine! Spice forward rather than five spice", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sichuan cold noodles tasted like they had been sitting in the fridge for a few hours—starch retrograded and the texture was off. Sauce was balanced and flavorful but the noodles were just wrong. Beef noodle soup was solidly fine! Spice forward rather than five spice", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Eth Wu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116506454754580022734/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUC9KtKriD2CrQE9-HQjzKsydaqTOhupbcqC9MBD3ormh8BWdMo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-29T04:25:18.935025234Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0cWFWTjFOWEZNUzFVelNVNWhNRkZaVUVOMlgyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0cWFWTjFOWEZNUzFVelNVNWhNRkZaVUVOMlgyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dab650970315:0xc4883287dace2398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFQOXULbawoARmCPO2ocyiMQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kSVNrWnpaVVoxTjFneGNtRk1NbU5WUlRWb1pVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Good value dishes. The spicy beef noodle soup was only $15 and the portions for the beef were pretty generous. Beef cuts varied between being very dry to somewhat tender. Noodles were fresh and chewy. Getting mild spicy was more spicy than I thought it would be right at the beginning, but over time I think I got used to the kick from the chilis.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Good value dishes. The spicy beef noodle soup was only $15 and the portions for the beef were pretty generous. Beef cuts varied between being very dry to somewhat tender. Noodles were fresh and chewy. Getting mild spicy was more spicy than I thought it would be right at the beginning, but over time I think I got used to the kick from the chilis.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "raymond mund", "